platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Play along with your favourite stars.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Not everyone can play like a proand thats OK. Pick a song and Magic Piano does the hard work for you. Theres something for everyone too, from Britney to Beethoven, and as you play youll unlock even more great tracks! Some of your favourite artists will even sing along with you as you show the world what youre made of.
